        "timestamp": 1772951917,
        "contenuto_esteso": "The US and Israel struck an oil depot in Tehran on Saturday. After attacking the regime's defence systems, the Israelins and Americans are attacking the regime's production sites and logistics. Satellite images show the extent of the devastation to port infrastructure. FRANCE 24's Olivier Faissolle and Daniel Quinlan have more."
